data.title: Celebrity Visitors
data.meta_description: For many years, from the time Graceland opened to the public on June 7, 1982, the tour guide staff informally kept a list of the celebrities who visited. View our current list.
data.text:
For many years, from the time Graceland opened to the public on June 7, 1982, the tour guide staff informally kept a list of the celebrities who visited. We’ve missed a few names along the way and, unfortunately, we did not always keep track of the dates. Once we created this feature for the web site, record-keeping of celebrity visits became a bit more formalized. Our list is updated continually as more celebrities visit and we continue to add names we missed from years past whenever someone recalls one. If you know of someone we missed and, please do let us know and we'll add the name if we can document the visit. In all the hubbub around here, word sometimes doesn't get to the web staff to post our latest celebrity visit. E-mails from fans to help out are always appreciated. Check out some of these photos!

Latest Additions:

October 13, 2023: band Toad the Wet Sprocket October 12, 2023: actor Warrick Davis; August 14, 2023: actor Lee Majors; January 8, 2023: actor Alton Mason and professional wrestler Shotzi Blackheart; November 12, 2022: actor and musicianFinn Wolfhard; Fall of 2022: actor and film producer Dwayne Johnson and actor and singer Uli Latukefu; October 29, 2022: "General Hospital" cast members Maurice Benard, Laura Wright, Tajh Bellow,Eden McCoy, Genie Francis,Brook Kerr, Katelyn MacMullen,Cameron Mathison, Avery Pohl, Dominic Zamprogna, Frank Valentini; October 22, 2022: Singer and Grammy Nominee Noah Cyrus; October 21, 2022: professional wrestler Chavo Guerrero; October 5, 2022: Ambassador of JordanDina Kawar; October 3, 2022: actor and model Ryan Pinkston and actor Benjamin Arthur; September 30, 2022: actress, comedian and former NFL cheerleader: Anjelah Johnson; July 8, 2022: "Young Elvis" in the ELVIS movie Chaydon Jay; June 22, 2022: HSN host John Rich; June 12, 2022: Producer and actor Jess Cagle, Reporter Chris Connelly, Canadian ice hockey player Wayne Gretzky, actress, singer and producer Rita Wilson and The "ELVIS" movie cast members and production team Catherine Martin, Baz Luhrmann, Austin Butler, Olivia Dejong, Tom Hanks, Alton Mason May 21, 2022: Italian rock band Måneskin; May 4, 2022: King of Ghana and many more below!!
